Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.62,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.82,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:51.33,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:57.82,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:04.33,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:10.75,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were here, and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:17.21,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:23.01,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:30.01,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it up, here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.84,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Be alive, take it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.22,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise to find, yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:45.54,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.74,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly high, make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:52.17,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:58.77,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 凭借自己那小小的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫回首 将悲伤留在身后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是我的真意所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿君伴我身侧 与我肩并肩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地包容我的自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在为自己的风格而上下求索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫轻言弃 这才是生命的真义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 莫放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信 自己必会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那满怀希望 熠熠生辉的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振翅高飞 翱翔九天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将去往自己所追寻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 我坚信
